371
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:28,190
I want to launch my shop in the mainland.

372
00:31:28,190 --> 00:31:30,310
Hawaii is just my testing ground.

373
00:31:30,950 --> 00:31:32,970
"Japanese Tea Rice"?

374
