What do you think?

377
00:32:02,300 --> 00:32:05,300
– It's quite ordinary.
– That's the point.

378
00:32:09,390 --> 00:32:10,650
Perhaps you should add
more variety to your menu?

379
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:14,480
No, that's won't work. My plan is
to launch my stores across the country.

380
00:32:14,740 --> 00:32:18,420
The States is teeming with
Japanese restaurant as it is.

381
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:23,270
I need to set my brand apart from
the others. It's tougher on the mainland.

382
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:24,380
I see.

383
00:32:25,540 --> 00:32:28,110
