she's divorced.

474
00:37:53,780 --> 00:37:55,840
You have to choose wisely, you know?

475
00:37:55,850 --> 00:38:01,700
I don't want a green card and
I'm not in a hurry to get married.

476
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:03,540
So you're all right with staying single?

477
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:08,840
I can't marry the guy I'm dating anyway.

478
00:38:09,330 --> 00:38:12,320
You're seeing someone?
Why can't you marry him?

479
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,620
– You mean he's already married?
– Drop it already.

480
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:20,970
There's nothing worse than cheating.

481
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:26,260
Okay, I'm so sorry.

482
00:38:26,690 --> 00:38:30,820
I'm only saying this in your best
interest. You better listen up.

483
00:38:30,940 --> 00:38:33,020
I hear you, Sis.

484
00:38:33,250 --> 00:38:35,550
But I don’t need you
pointing out all my faults.

485
00:38:35,550 --> 00:38:39,630
I'm not looking to settle down
and I don't intend to marry for money.

486
00:38:39,890 --> 00:38:43,400
Neither do I. But you've got to
start looking somewhere, don't you?

487
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:45,630
I'm just starting with the rich.

488
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:47,720
Why the rich?

489
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:50,020
Minori, you think all rich people
are jerks, don't you?

490
00:38:50,150 --> 00:38:51,410
That's discrimination.

491
00:38:51,410 --> 00:38:55,180
Yeah. While you don't discriminate,
you'll sleep with anyone.

492
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,810
What's that supposed to mean?

493
00:38:56,870 --> 00:39:00,230
You're the one crashing parties
to mount rich tycoons.

494
00:39:00,230 --> 00:39:01,480
That was just innocent fun.

495
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:02,730
What about Honma?

496
00:39:02,730 --> 00:39:04,050
