00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:10,240
What?

501
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:13,280
I've only slept with Honma.

502
00:39:13,790 --> 00:39:15,510
In fact, he's my first.

503
00:39:16,380 --> 00:39:19,300
That's why he's always on my back.
I think he feels responsible.

504
00:39:20,870 --> 00:39:21,610
Eh?

505
00:39:23,620 --> 00:39:26,130
Why are you so surprised?
What kind of person did you think I was?

506
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:29,700
Well... I mean...

507
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:33,090
What about all those men?

508
00:39:33,390 --> 00:39:34,720
I didn't sleep with any of them!

509
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:39,460
I don't have affairs with married men or
go to their place on the first date!

